name: SKYZONE- JON WALTZ, JAMEE CORNELIA, & JADYN VIOLET

metadata.description:
Skyzone started in 2020 with an entirely different sounding record, I felt like the sound was too experimental when the homie Eric (from 4km) started it but then I revisited the record in 2022 and knew exactly who to reach out to: Jamee Cornelia and Jadyn Violet. Jamee came in with an absolutely infectious energy and such a superstar verse, then Jadyn laced the record with some beautiful melodies and I went back in and redid my verse and we had a whole ass bop 



Written by Jon Waltz, Jamee Cornelia & Jadyn Violet 

Prod by 4km

Artwork by Jules Lauber
metadata.name: SKYZONE- JON WALTZ, JAMEE CORNELIA, & JADYN VIOLET
